defaultVSO aims to support disabled people to participate as equal members of their families, communities and societies. Volunteers are supporting local agencies and governments to identify strategies that promote disabled people's human rights, such as education, employment and healthcare.  We do this by supporting disabled people's groups to raise awareness of issues that affect disabled people, and working to improve the accessibility and quality of mainstream and special services provided by both the government and by non-governmental organi
